text: Marcel Henry (30 October 1926 – 30 August 2021) was a French politician. He was born in Mayotte, France. He was a member of the French Senate from 1977 until 2004.Marcel Henry , Portrait d'hommes politiques de Mayotte, Malango Mayotte. Updated 27 September 2009. Retrieved 11 May 2010.Marcel Henry - Ancien sénateur de Mayotte, Anciens sénateurs Ve République, French Senate. Retrieved 11 May 2010. He was one of the founders of the Mahoré People's Movement. Henry died on 30 August 2021 at the age of 94. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:2021 deaths Category:French politicians Category:People from Mayotte
